WarmDirt - The Greenhouse Box Temperature Controller

Here's a greenhouse box temperature controller for winter growing.

Requirements
    Sensors
        Temperature 
            Heated dirt
            Potted dirt
            Box interior air
            Box exterior air
        Humidity 
            Box Interior
        Ambient light
        Lid closed switch
        Heater current monitor

    Control
        Heater
        DC Motor

    Communication
        XBEE

    Framework
        Arduino compatible using ATMEGA328P
        


ATMEGA328P pin mapping

                                    +-\/-+
        /RESET                PC6  1|    |28  PC5 (AI 5)     ADC5 SCL PCINT13
        RXD             (D 0) PD0  2|    |27  PC4 (AI 4)     ADC4 SDA PCINT12
        TXD             (D 1) PD1  3|    |26  PC3 (AI 3)     ADC3 
ENCA    INT0            (D 2) PD2  4|    |25  PC2 (AI 2)     ADC2 Int  Temp
ENCB    INT1            (D 3) PD3  5|    |24  PC1 (AI 1)     ADC1 Pot  Temp
                        (D 4) PD4  6|    |23  PC0 (AI 0)     ADC0 Dirt Temp
                              VCC  7|    |22  GND
                              GND  8|    |21  AREF
        XTAL1                 PB6  9|    |20  AVCC
        XTAL2                 PB7 10|    |19  PB5 (D 13)     SCK      PCINT5
PCINT21 OCOB T1    PWM+ (D 5) PD5 11|    |18  PB4 (D 12)     MISO     PCINT4
PCINT22 OC0A AIN0  PWM+ (D 6) PD6 12|    |17  PB3 (D 11) PWM MOSI     PCINT3
PCINT23      AIN1       (D 7) PD7 13|    |16  PB2 (D 10) PWM /SS OC1B PCINT2
PCINT0 CLK0  ICP1       (D 8) PB0 14|    |15  PB1 (D 9)  PWM     OC1A PCINT1
                                    +----+



P
1   PD3 (PCINT19/OC2B/INT1)
2   PD4 (PCINT20/XCK/T0) 
3   GND
4   VCC
5   GND
6   VCC
7   PB6 (PCINT6/XTAL1/TOSC1) 
8   PB7 (PCINT7/XTAL2/TOSC2) 

9   PD5 (PCINT21/OC0B/T1) PD5
10  PD6 (PCINT22/OC0A/AIN0) PD6
11  PD7 (PCINT23/AIN1) PD7
12  (PCINT0/CLKO/ICP1) PB0
13  (PCINT1/OC1A) PB1
14  (PCINT2/SS/OC1B) PB2
15  (PCINT3/OC2A/MOSI) PB3
16  (PCINT4/MISO) PB4

17  PB5 (SCK/PCINT5)
18  AVCC
19  ADC6
20  AREF
21  GND
22  ADC7
23  PC0 (ADC0/PCINT8)
24  PC1 (ADC1/PCINT9)

25  PC2 (ADC2/PCINT10)
26  PC3 (ADC3/PCINT11)
27  PC4 (ADC4/SDA/PCINT12)
28  PC5 (ADC5/SCL/PCINT13)
29  PC6 (RESET/PCINT14)
30  PD0 (RXD/PCINT16)
31  PD1 (TXD/PCINT17)
32  PD2 (INT0/PCINT18)
